cell::Cell::<T>::get.doc:
Returns a copy of the contained value.

# Examples

```
use std::cell::Cell;

let c = Cell::new(5);

let five = c.get();
```

cell::Cell::<T>::set.doc:
Sets the contained value.

# Examples

```
use std::cell::Cell;

let c = Cell::new(5);

c.set(10);
```

